  "body": "The deposit contract itself is in the Eth1 chain.\r\n\r\nNeed to add an interface / way for an Eth1 watcher to push new Eth1Data into the beacon node as needed (as it appears on the Eth1 chain).\r\n\r\nThis interface can have alternative implementations. For testing, the mocked start details from Eth2 Project Management (PM) as a way to test arrival of Eth1 data.\r\n\r\nAnother implementation can interface with Nethermind Eth1.\r\n\r\nMaybe also provide an implementation that can lookup an Internet source / Eth1 block explorer to get the data, for people not running local Nethereum Eth1.",
